OL,3,CNew cash for the Welsh NHS but is it
OL,4,Cenough?
OL,6,FThe new Welsh Government is facing
OL,7,Fscepticism over a #145m NHS funding
OL,8,Fboost, with critics questioning
OL,9,Fwhether the top-up can make any dent
OL,10,Fin a system costing #12bn a year.
OL,12,FFigures published on Thursday showed
OL,13,Fthat in April - the Welsh Labour
OL,14,Fgovernment's final month in charge -
OL,15,Fthere was a rise in the number of
OL,16,Fpeople waiting for treatment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1781871073
OL,3,CNew cash for the Welsh NHS but is it
OL,4,Cenough?
OL,6,FThere were also more people waiting
OL,7,Ffor longer than two years - a backlog
OL,8,Fthe new Health Minister insists will
OL,9,Fbe eradicated "within a matter of
OL,10,Fmonths" after previously saying it
OL,11,Fcould take four years.
OL,13,FThe funding will be spent on bringing
OL,14,Fdown waiting lists, building new
OL,15,Fsurgical and diagnostic hubs and
OL,16,Fessential maintenance to the estate.
OL,18,FBut with health costing the previous
OL,19,FWelsh Government #12.3bn in one year,
OL,20,Fhow far can #145m really go?
OL,26,@qD@OOUrD@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
