OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1781871073
OL,3,CNew cash for the Welsh NHS but is it
OL,4,Cenough?
OL,6,FTake waiting times. A year ago, the
OL,7,Fformer Welsh Labour Health Secretary
OL,8,FJeremy Miles announced #120m to cut
OL,9,Fthese. The overall waiting list then
OL,10,Ffell consistently for 10 months.
OL,12,FBut Thursday's figures show that trend
OL,13,Fhas reversed, something the new Health
OL,14,FMinister Mabon ap Gwynfor puts down to
OL,15,Fa "sticking plaster approach" by his
OL,16,Fpredecessors.
OL,26,@wD@COUwD@]O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1781871073
OL,3,CNew cash for the Welsh NHS but is it
OL,4,Cenough?
OL,6,FThat's something that Welsh Labour
OL,7,Fdispute, arguing that: "...since the
OL,8,FWelsh Labour Government's #120m
OL,9,Finvestment in June of last year, the
OL,10,Faverage wait for treatment is now the
OL,11,Fshortest on record since the pandemic."
OL,13,FThe Health Minister claims Plaid Cymru
OL,14,Fis doing things differently: "They
OL,15,Fdidn't build capacity into the system.
OL,16,FThat's why we had these repeat issues
OL,17,Fwhere waiting lists were coming down
OL,18,Fbut (going) back up again.
OL,26,@vD@^OUzD@EpmzD@Kpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1781871073
OL,3,CNew cash for the Welsh NHS but is it
OL,4,Cenough?
OL,6,F"We're putting money earlier into the
OL,7,Fsystem and early intervention on
OL,8,Fidentifying the diagnostics, improving
OL,9,Fthe pathways so that people don't
OL,10,Freach that point where they are
OL,11,Flanguishing for a long time on a
OL,12,Fwaiting list."
OL,14,FPart of that, he said, is the #25m
OL,15,Finvestment in 10 new surgical and
OL,16,Fdiagnostic hubs. But he could not yet
OL,17,Ftell us where those centres will be
OL,18,Fbuilt.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@NO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
