CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1781871073
OL,3,CNew cash for the Welsh NHS but is it
OL,4,Cenough?
OL,6,FAnd when they are built, who will
OL,7,Fstaff them? While welcoming additional
OL,8,Ffunding, the Royal College of Nursing
OL,9,Fhas today raised concerns over
OL,10,Fworkforce plans.
OL,12,F"Nursing staff are telling us
OL,13,Fconsistently and across Wales that
OL,14,Fdespite there being no vacancies there
OL,15,Fis insufficient staff to meet
OL,16,Fincreasing patient complexity and
OL,17,Fdemand and nurses are going without
OL,18,Fbreaks and feel most shifts that they
OL,19,Fare unable to give the care that
OL,20,Fpatients' need," said Wales Executive
OL,21,FDirector Nicola Williams.
OL,26,@tD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
