PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1781871073
OL,3,CNew cash for the Welsh NHS but is it
OL,4,Cenough?
OL,6,F"Delivering sustainable improvements
OL,7,Fdepends on having the right,
OL,8,Fappropriately trained and skilled
OL,9,Fworkforce in places and nurses will
OL,10,Fplay a pivotal role in the provision
OL,11,Fof safe, effective and efficient care
OL,12,Fto ensure that the surgical and
OL,13,Fdiagnostic hubs fully achieve the
OL,14,Fambition. Therefore, funding robust
OL,15,Fworkforce modelling and plans is
OL,16,Fcritically important "
OL,18,FThen there is the #20m for "essential
OL,19,Fmaintenance across the NHS estate".
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@\OU{D@bO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
