CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1781871073
OL,3,CNew cash for the Welsh NHS but is it
OL,4,Cenough?
OL,6,FIn March, ITV Wales revealed sewage
OL,7,Fleaks, broken equipment and failing
OL,8,Fventilation were leading to cancelled
OL,9,Foperations and appointments, including
OL,10,Fat Wales' largest and most specialist
OL,11,Fin Cardiff.
OL,13,FAn estimated #1.4bn was the cost to
OL,14,Ffix maintenance issues across Wales'
OL,15,FNHS estate between 2024-2025.
OL,17,FWhen asked whether #20m was anywhere
OL,18,Fnear enough to address those issues,
OL,19,Fthe Health Minister suggested the
OL,20,Fmoney would be spent on new equipment
OL,21,Fsuch as mobile CT scanners.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1781871073
OL,3,CNew cash for the Welsh NHS but is it
OL,4,Cenough?
OL,6,FWhile the Welsh Conservatives welcomed
OL,7,Fnew funding, their Shadow Health
OL,8,FMinister Natasha Asghar argued that
OL,9,FPlaid Cymru must share the blame for
OL,10,FNHS performance, having "propped up
OL,11,Fthe previous Welsh Labour government
OL,12,Fby backing their budgets".
OL,14,FJust a month into the job, the
OL,15,Fgovernment has promised further action
OL,16,Fwithin its first 100 days - including
OL,17,Fnaming the clinicians designing the
OL,18,Fnew hubs and mapping out where 100
OL,19,Fpromised new GPs will be deployed.
OL,26,@rD@YOUtD@YO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/10
